tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE tv_shows (
    show_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    show_name TEXT,
    genre TEXT,
    release_date DATE
);
CREATE TABLE viewership (
    viewer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    show_id INT,
    viewer_name TEXT,
    age INT,
    gender TEXT,
    viewing_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (show_id) REFERENCES tv_shows(show_id)
);

CREATE TABLE TV_Show_Views (
    show_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    show_name TEXT,
    viewer_id INT,
    viewer_name TEXT,
    viewing_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Viewership_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    show_id INT,
    viewer_id INT,
    rating FLOAT,
    date_watched DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Ratings (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    rating_id INT,
    show_id INT,
    rating_value FLOAT,
    rating_date DATE
);
